CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 29, 1958, pg. 7, reads: "Attention State Liquor Control Board - How Many More Taverns Can Homewood-Brushton Stand? On Hamilton Ave. - Among the seven public liquor dispensing establishments on Hamilton Ave. are (left photo): Lou's [Louie's] Bar and Grill, in the 7200 block... - All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Louie's Bar and Grill and parked cars, 7200 block of Hamilton Avenue, Homewood
